c: 3
v: 199
t: "Inene phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi kukho abo bakholwayo kuAllâh nakoko kutyhilwe kuwe (wena Muhammad) nakoko kwatyhilwa kubo, bayazithoba phambi koAllâh. Abathengisi ngeeVesi zika-Allâh ngexabiso elincinane, okwabo iya kuba ngumvuzo ovela eNkosini yabo. Inene uAllâh Uyakhawuleza ukufaka embuzweni"